- Pydantic [Bookmark](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/storage/bookmark_model.py#14-52) model: [author](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/extractor/tweet_extractor.py#73-94), [text](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/browser/browser_manager.py#86-92), `url`, [images](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/tests/test_bookmark_model.py#43-54), [thread](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/tests/test_bookmark_model.py#81-97)

