## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

#### [NEW] [tests/test_bookmark_model.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/tests/test_bookmark_model.py)
- Unit tests for [Bookmark](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/storage/bookmark_model.py#14-52) model validation (valid/invalid data)

#### [NEW] [tests/test_json_store.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/tests/test_json_store.py)
- Unit tests for JSON save/load and deduplication logic using temp files

#### [NEW] [tests/test_retry.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/tests/test_retry.py)
- Unit tests for the retry decorator (success, exhaustion, specific exception types)

#### [NEW] [tests/test_config.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/tests/test_config.py)
- Unit tests for config defaults and [.env](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/.env) override loading

**Run all tests with:**
```
uv run python -m pytest tests/ -v
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> End-to-end testing against live X (Twitter) requires a valid account with bookmarks. The automated unit tests above validate the core logic in isolation. The full scraping flow must be verified manually by the user with their own credentials.

### Manual Verification (User)
1. Run `uv run python main.py`
2. If no [session.json](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/session.json) exists, it will prompt for X username and password — enter valid credentials
3. Observe logs showing login, navigation to bookmarks, scroll progress, and extraction count
4. Confirm [data/bookmarks.json](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/data/bookmarks.json) is created with the correct structure
5. Re-run and verify session reuse (no login prompt)
